OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDespite
OL,6,Flargely clear skies many places will
OL,7,Fhave another warm or very warm night,
OL,8,Fespecially in large towns and cities,
OL,9,Fwith the humid conditions persisting.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FSunny inland, with perhaps
OL,12,Fpatchy low cloud and mist reaching the
OL,13,Fcoast, especially northern coasts,
OL,14,FBecoming breezy with the easterly
OL,15,Fwinds keeping coastal areas cooler,
OL,16,Fhighest temperatures in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
