OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHot or
OL,6,Fvery hot Friday, thereafter
OL,7,Ftemperatures decreasing. Bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells Friday and Saturday,
OL,9,Fchance of thunderstorms, mainly
OL,10,FSaturday night. Cloudier Sunday,
OL,11,Fpatchy light rain possible.
